response.overview: An event of galactic proportions, Power Pro Lucha is back for our third showing in The City of Brotherly Love on July 19, 2025!  What secrets will be uncovered this time around? How exactly does UltraMantis Black intend to accept Tim Donst’s challenge? What did The Devious One mean by “on his terms”? Who will step up to be the first challenger for Harleen Lopez’s Prodigy Cup? Will Mr. Nicodemus’ newest creation, Fenris, strike again? Does Poisynhawk intend to continue to make life difficult for The Xyberhawx? We hope to learn all of this—and more!
response.title: Power Pro Lucha: Power Bomb
